r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'Web Application', 'http://hsinlei.com', 'blue', '0', '0', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-05-06 02:06:58', '2015-09-05 00:16:40', '75ff3a9c-f4da-4a67-8051-e0efe173d286');
