m to learn, share and resonate with other people with same interests and experiences.\\r\\n<\\/p><p>The key concept to understand is that <strong>motivation<\\/strong> is difficult to change. Don\'t focus on it. Rewards are great but not effective <strong>unless they perform the behavior first.<\\/strong>\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"39\":\"\",\"23\":\"Reaserch & Analysis\",\"20\":\"<p>I led the website UX design for ACCPI community site. The goal is to reshape the LivePerson\'s (LP) brand\\u2019s online presence, through creating a sleek sharable community experiences and transferring the site focus to nurturing a customer care professional which would offer more engaging online experiences for customers. As a IA and UX person, I conducted researches and came up with a series of ideations before planning and restructuring the site, followed by important considerations from both design and development point of view. Here is a work in progress for ACCPI website.<br><\\/p><ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Research & analysis<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>IA & sitemap<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Persona<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Use flow<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Wireframes<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Interactive prototype<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Testing<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul><p>My Objectives include<br><\\/p><ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Gathers a thriving global profession of best-in-class customer cares experts across all industries, and LP also influences the community by sharing knowledge and provides trainings as industry lead;<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Builds up a member-driven organization committed to promoting customer care and customer engagement as a competitive advantage in business;<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>This website can be a soft sale tool that Introduce LP\'s 2.0 platform, mobile applications and its benefits;<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"19\":\"Project Brief\",\"10\":\"LivePerson\",\"11\":\"http:\\/\\/www.liveperson.com\\/\",\"58\":\"yellow\",\"25\":{\"185\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Persona\",\"body\":\"<p>In order to demostrate our target audience for ACCPI, I\'ve created 5 personas, here list two as examples. Their working experience level as a customer care professional is about junior to mid-weight. Full persona list and analysis will be provided by request.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"182\",\"183\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"\"}}},\"49\":\"Web Design\",\"14\":\"ACCPI\\r\\nCommunity Website\",\"22\":\"<p>I have taken this project from half-way, and the idea, use flow and even marketing strategy has been changed a lot from our original plan. To coincide with the a series of the campaign, our team was under extreme pressure to move fast. We were tasked to deliver from ideation to high\\u2010fidelity prototype to our technical production partner within 4 weeks, so it requires quick turnarounds. The combination of a fixed deadline, content strategy, usability testing, and usability testing meant I needed to get the experience right in the first two weeks.<\\/p>\",\"21\":\"What I\'ve Learned\",\"43\":[\"18\"],\"17\":\" I have taken this project from half-way, and the idea, use flow and even marketing strategy has been changed a lot from our original plan.\",\"18\":\"\",\"16\":\"ACCPI Community Website\",\"13\":[\"7\"],\"42\":[\"17\"],\"50\":\"https:\\/\\/accpi.org\\/\",\"44\":[\"16\"],\"12\":\"Researches, Wireframes, UX Design & Testing\",\"3\":\" I have taken this project from half-way, and the idea, use flow and even marketing strategy has been changed a lot from our original plan.\",\"9\":[\"photoshop\",\"axure\",\"sketch\"],\"4\":\"2015\"}}', '2015-08-25 03:45:00', '2015-08-25 03:45:00', '7c6aead3-3eda-4fe4-ad63-d9601c725366');
