ist two as examples. Their working experience level as a customer care professional is about junior to mid-weight. Full persona list and analysis will be provided by request.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"182\",\"183\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"User Flow\",\"body\":\"<p>Back to my analysis before, I think the community will be relatively open unless visitor wants to take action. The trigger can be the game, the social press of our community but most important, the ACCPI website content itself.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"188\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"1\"},\"collapsed\":\"\"},\"187\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Sitemap\",\"body\":\"<p>Back to my analysis before, I think the community will be relatively open unless visitor wants to take action. The trigger can be the game, the social press of our community but most important, the ACCPI website content itself.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"186\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"1\"}}},\"49\":\"Web Design\",\"14\":\"ACCPI\\r\\nCommunity Website\",\"22\":\"<p>I have taken this project from half-way, and the idea, use flow and even marketing strategy has been changed a lot from our original plan. To coincide with the a series of the campaign, our team was under extreme pressure to move fast. We were tasked to deliver from ideation to high\\u2010fidelity prototype to our technical production partner within 4 weeks, so it requires quick turnarounds. The combination of a fixed deadline, content strategy, usability testing, and usability testing meant I needed to get the experience right in the first two weeks.<\\/p>\",\"21\":\"What I\'ve Learned\",\"43\":[\"18\"],\"17\":\" I have taken this project from half-way, and the idea, use flow and even marketing strategy has been changed a lot from our original plan.\",\"18\":\"\",\"16\